These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: mystery, zombie, documentary, thriller, horror
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: hip-hop, salsa, d&b, folk, gospel
1. the fan of folk is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1
5. the fan of gospel is on the far left##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is in the middle##1
7. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |   5    |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | documentary | mystery | horror | thriller |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | hip-hop | d&b     | folk       | salsa  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-2::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, juice, milk, lemonade
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: techno, funk, salsa, pop, blues
1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the fan of funk##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking 7up is in the middle##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the fan of salsa##1
6. the fan of blues is the person drinking lemonade##1
7. the fan of pop is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |      3      |    4     |   5    |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | juice | 7up | milk | lemonade |
| Music-Genre   | salsa  | pop   | techno       | funk    | blues   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-3::.
There 5 different types of food: papaya, peach, lettuce, grapes, artichoke
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, car, skateboard, bike, van
1. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
2. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person driving the van##1
3. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
4. the person eating lettuce is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
6. the person eating peach is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Food        | lettuce | grapes | peach | papaya | artichoke |
| Transport   | car  | airplane      | van | skateboard | bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-4::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: skydiving, rock-climbing, dancing, photography, video-games
The people have 5 different jobs:  lawyer, journalist, accountant, police-officer, teacher
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the journalist##1
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the journalist##1
3. the police-officer is on the right of the lawyer##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the teacher##1
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
6. the accountant is on the far right##1
7. the teacher is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3    |    4    |     5     |
| Hobby   | photography    | skydiving        | dancing | rock-climbing | video-games |
| Job     | lawyer | police-officer | teacher  | journalist   | accountant |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-5::.
There 5 different types of food: lemon, radish, pear, apricot, blueberry
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: skiing, skateboarding, baseball, golf, basketball
1. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person eating pear##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person eating blueberry##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
4. the person who's sport is baseball is in the middle##1
5. the person eating pear is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
6. the person who's sport is basketball is the person eating apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |       4       |     5      |
| Food    | pear   | lemon     | radish   | apricot         | blueberry |
| Sport   | skiing | golf | baseball | basketball | skateboarding     |

