.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: swimming, motorbikeing, soccer, basketball, cycling
The people use 5 different means of transport: trike, tram, subway, snowmobile, motorbike
1. the person driving the snowmobile is in the middle##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the person driving the subway is the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is motorbikeing##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |     5     |
| Sport       | basketball   | soccer   | motorbikeing | cycling | swimming |
| Transport   | tram | subway | snowmobile   | motorbike | trike       |

