.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-7::.
5 different pets are kept: cat, bird, turtle, hamster, goldfish
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: skiing, golf, basketball, snowboarding, swimming
1. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is the owner of the cat##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is in the middle##1
6. the person who's sport is basketball is the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5      |
| Pet     | bird   | turtle  | goldfish      | cat | hamster     |
| Sport   | snowboarding | basketball | golf | skiing   | swimming |

