.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-8::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  project-manager, police-officer, software-developer, coach, librarian
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, golf, handball, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the librarian##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
4. the librarian is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
6. the project-manager is on the right of the police-officer##1
7. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the coach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |
| Job     | police-officer | project-manager       | librarian | coach | software-developer    |
| Sport   | handball   | skateboarding | golf  | cycling     | cricket |

