.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-9::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: drawing, soul-climbing, cooking, video-games, singing
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: d&b, hip-hop, electronic, punk, soul
1. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
3. the person who's hobby is soul-climbing is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left##1
5. the fan of soul is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is the fan of hip-hop##1
7. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3       |      4      |    5    |
| Hobby         | video-games | drawing | cooking | singing | soul-climbing |
| Music-Genre   | electronic       | punk   | soul         | hip-hop   | d&b   |

