.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-10::.
There are 5 different nationalities: canadian, french, turkish, mexican, polish
5 different pets are kept: turtle, rabbit, goat, guinea-pig, horse
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the french##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the turkish##1
3. the owner of the goat is the canadian##1
4. the mexican is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is in the middle##1
6. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |    5     |
| Nationality   | polish | mexican | french | turkish | canadian |
| Pet           | horse      | rabbit    | guinea-pig  | turtle     | goat     |

