3. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
5. the person eating zucchini is on the far right##1
6. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
7. the owner of the hamster is the person eating peach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |   2    |    3    |     4     |      5      |
| Food   | radish | cauliflower  | peach | apricot | zucchini |
| Pet    | horse    | mouse | hamster   | bird       | turtle        |

