.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-12::.
There 5 different types of food: pear, lime, orange, avocado, papaya
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: baseball, skateboarding, volleyball, basketball, rowing
1. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
2. the person eating avocado is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person eating lime##1
4. the person eating lime is on the far right##1
5. the person eating orange is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person eating lime##1
7. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3     |    4    |    5    |
| Food    | pear | avocado          | orange    | papaya | lime  |
| Sport   | volleyball  | rowing | baseball | basketball | skateboarding |

