.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-13::.
There are 5 different nationalities: brazilian, argentine, indonesian, american, malaysian
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, boat, skateboard, quad-bike, jet-ski
1. the argentine is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the boat is the brazilian##1
4. the malaysian is the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the brazilian##1
6. the american is in the middle##1
7. the american is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |    4     |    5    |
| Nationality   | indonesian | brazilian      | american | argentine | malaysian |
| Transport     | quad-bike  | boat | helicopter     | jet-ski     | skateboard  |

