4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the brazilian##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | water | iced-tea | milk      | mirinda | almond-milk      |
| Nationality   | egyptian  | pakistani       | brazilian | chinese  | polish |

