.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-18::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: crime, documentary, horror, martial-arts, thriller
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: skateboarding, lacrosse, cycling, biathlon, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is in the middle##1
2. the person watching crime movies is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4      |    5     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary   | martial-arts  | crime | thriller | horror  |
| Sport         | skateboarding | cycling | biathlon  | volleyball    | lacrosse |

