.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-19::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, lemonade, coffee, cola
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: rugby, soccer, skiing, water-polo, cycling
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is skiing is the person drinking coffee##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
6. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |   4    |    5     |
| Beverage   | cola     | lemonade       | iced-tea     | juice  | coffee  |
| Sport      | water-polo | rugby | soccer | cycling | skiing |

