.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-20::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: epic, family, zombie, action, crime
5 different pets are kept: goldfish, horse, hedgehog, snake, fish
1. the owner of the horse is in the middle##1
2. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
6. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |    3    |      4      |   5    |
| Movie-Genre   | family | crime | zombie | epic | action |
| Pet           | fish | snake  | horse    | goldfish  | hedgehog   |

 